These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, french, polish
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, pony, bird
1. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the australian##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the french##3
4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the polish is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the pakistani is somewhere between the australian and the owner of the mouse##7
8. the pakistani and the owner of the bird have the same parity positions##9
9. the french and the owner of the chinchilla have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani | french     | polish |
| Pet           | pony   | bird     | mouse | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, mirinda, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, reading, photography
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is photography and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
7. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | mirinda    | sprite | 7up    |
| Hobby      | collecting | video-games | reading      | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, mirinda, water
There 4 different types of food: plum, onion, pineapple, peach
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
2. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person eating plum##1
7. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
8. the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating onion have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | mirinda   | iced-tea    | water  |
| Food       | onion | peach | plum | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, paramedic, social-worker, manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, soul, funk, techno
1. the fan punk is the paramedic##1
2. the fan soul is on the right of the fan funk##1
3. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
4. the fan techno is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
5. the fan soul is on the left of the videographer##1
6. the manager and the fan techno have the same parity positions##9
7. the social-worker is on the left or right of the videographer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | manager | social-worker | videographer  | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | funk             | soul          | techno | punk    |

