.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, r&b, salsa, gospel
4 different pets are kept: fish, horse, bird, rat
1. the fan salsa is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the owner of the fish and the fan dubstep have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the horse and the fan r&b have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan gospel##1
6. the fan r&b is not the owner of the horse##6
7. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
9. the owner of the rat is not the fan gospel##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | salsa | gospel  | r&b |
| Pet           | horse   | fish     | bird | rat      |

