3. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
4. the egyptian and the person watching family movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching drama movies and the egyptian have different parity positions##9
6. the turkish is not to the left of the person watching horror movies##8
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the indonesian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | horror | family | drama |
| Nationality   | indonesian        | turkish    | egyptian   | japanese |

