2. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is tennis##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball and the fan dubstep have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the fan dubstep is not to the right of the fan indie##8
6. the fan trance is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
7. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan metal##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | trance | dubstep         | indie     |
| Sport         | rugby | volleyball  | tennis | rowing |

