4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, dog, horse
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
7. the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the horse have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | puzzles | magic-tricks | dancing |
| Pet     | guinea-pig     | dog     | horse     | hedgehog    |

