.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, tomato, cauliflower, cucumber
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, roller, van
1. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
2. the person eating cucumber and the person driving the van have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the van##7
6. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | cauliflower | kale   | tomato | cucumber |
| Transport   | roller   | quad-bike | ship    | van      |

