.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pear, banana, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, chinese, polish, american
1. the person eating lettuce is not the american##6
2. the american is not to the right of the egyptian##8
3. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the polish##3
6. the american is on the far left##1
7. the egyptian is on the left of the person eating banana##1
8. the person eating orange is the chinese##1
9. the person eating lettuce and the egyptian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pear   | lettuce    | banana | orange    |
| Nationality   | american | egyptian | polish   | chinese |

