2. the fan blues is not to the left of the person eating cherry##8
3. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the fan r&b and the fan blues##7
4. the fan blues is somewhere between the fan folk and the person eating cauliflower##7
5. the fan trance is not the person eating zucchini##6
6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | zucchini | cauliflower | cherry | watermelon  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | trance | blues | folk |

