.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, action, western
1. the person watching thriller movies is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
8. the person watching thriller movies and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching action movies and the person drinking mirinda have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk  | mirinda  | milk |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action | western | thriller      |

