The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, disco, folk
 1. the person drinking tea and the fan disco have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 3. the fan house is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking coffee##7
 4. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan disco is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the person drinking cola and the fan hip-hop have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 9. the fan folk is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan house##8

