2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the teacher is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
4. the nurse is not to the right of the coach##8
5. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the snake and the software-developer have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the lizard and the teacher have the same parity positions##9

