.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, mirinda, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, singing, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is collecting have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | iced-tea | fanta | 7up |
| Hobby      | singing | collecting   | chess   | woodworking   |

