.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, video-games, card-games
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is singing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is singing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | milk        | soy-milk   | mirinda      |
| Hobby      | card-games | video-games | singing | woodworking |

 